00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:05,240
We found two old cases in which
Vishwambharan was involved.

493
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:08,320
To hell with it.
Throw it away.

494
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,960
We don't require it anymore.

495
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:15,280
He is now transforming
himself into a Gandhian.

496
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:19,240
Discard this file
and start a new one.

497
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,960
Whose?
- Guptan's.

498
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:22,600
Guptan, the one who is dead?

499
00:37:22,640 --> 00:37:24,880
We are not able to find the details

500
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:26,960
of the living,
let alone this dead guy.

501
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,560
We have to find it immediately.

502
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,840
Harikrishnans Associates!

503
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:37,960
Networks all over India!

504
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:40,360
And yet, nobody could find
any details about Guptan.

505
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:42,760
There is absolutely no information!

506
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:43,720
Nonsense!

507
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,360
Did he fall from the sky?

508
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:49,840
We received the specimen
re-examination report from Delhi.

509
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:53,160
They couldn't identify the
details about the poison yet.

510
00:37:53,240 --> 00:37:54,200
Not yet?
- No.

511
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,560
Where is this case heading to?

512
00:37:57,680 --> 00:37:58,560
Did you tell Hari?
- Yes.

513
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:03,400
It seems that Guptan doesn't
belong to this planet.

514
00:38:03,560 --> 00:38:05,440
It seems that he came
from some other planet.

515
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:09,240
Did you inquire about Mira's
cousin, Mr. Kunjikuttan?

516
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:12,160
He is good for nothing.
Should we inquire about him?

517
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:13,560
No, leave him alone for now.

518
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:15,400
He might send for us.

519
00:38:15,560 --> 00:38:18,240
But Guptan.. - We cannot even
find his address.

520
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:20,360
It's Guptan, care of Mira
at the police station.

521
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:22,000
It's Guptan, care of Mira
at the hotel.

522
00:38:22,120 --> 00:38:23,880
It's Guptan, care of Mira
even in the post-mortem report.

523
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:26,600
Only while receiving his body,
it's written as Mira.

524
00:38:27,960 --> 00:38:28,960
What could be a solution for this?

525
00:38:30,560 --> 00:38:31,960
How many ambulances would
be there in Poonoor?

526
00:38:33,520 --> 00:38:34,720
I didn't think in that way.

527
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,520
Now you have to start
thinking in that way.

528
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:44,640
Who are you?
- Are you an ambulance driver?

529
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:49,840
Antony, right?
- Yes.

530
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:55,640
Guptan's body was
taken in your ambulance

531
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:58,240
after the post-mortem
on the 27th of last month.

532
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:02,120
I don't know anyone called Guptan.

533
00:39:04,200 --> 00:39:07,840
We have lots of work
to do after this.

534
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:09,040
Try to remember.

535
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:11,800
I deal with dead bodies every day.

536
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:12,880
I never remember these things.

537
00:39:16,560 --> 00:39:17,680
Now, just try to remember it.

538
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,560
Yes, try to remember.
Just think about it.

539
00:39:21,640 --> 00:39:23,080
Come on, Antony.
Tell us.

540
00:39:23,560 --> 00:39:24,680
Tell us.
- Yes, I will.

541
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:28,640
Mira had told me to keep it
as a secret. - That's okay.

542
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:30,280
I took it to a place
200 km away from here.

543
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:31,160
Where?

544
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:33,160
To the Killikal palace.

545
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,560
Killikal palace.

546
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:47,240
"Magical palace."

547
00:39:51,280 --> 00:39:53,200
Oh, God!

548
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:57,320
Who are you?
- We are Guptan's..

549
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,440
Why are you

550
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:01,680
trying to scare us?

551
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:03,920
I was scared.

552
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:07,720
We are advocates
enquiring about Guptan.

553
00:40:08,240 --> 00:40:09,200
Who lives here?

554
00:40:09,240 --> 00:40:12,360
Myself, my Lord and a servant.
That's all.

555
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:14,360
So are you the youngest of the lot?

556
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:18,240
In a way. - So are you
not directly related? - No.

557
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:23,880
So let the Lord know that two
advocates are here to meet him.

558
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:32,600
'This magnificent evening.'

559
00:40:33,520 --> 00:40:35,120
Hari.
- Yes?

560
00:40:35,320 --> 00:40:37,240
'This magnificent evening.'

561
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:38,320
Keep it..

562
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:41,280
What is it now?

563
00:40:43,600 --> 00:40:44,440
Who are you?

564
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:47,120
Why do you want to meet me?

565
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:51,200
They want to ask the same
questions and hurt me. That's all.

566
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:54,440
What's the use in talking now?

567
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:56,560
Can you give my Guptan back to me?

568
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:57,800
Can you?

569
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:04,280
The ones who murdered
my innocent son

570
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:07,160
are freely walking the streets.

571
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:11,040
Can you get them to me alive?

572
00:41:11,120 --> 00:41:12,640
You may talk to me after that.

573
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:13,680
Can you?

574
00:41:15,000 --> 00:41:17,200
We will present

575
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:18,480
whoever is responsible
for your son's death

576
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:20,720
at your feet

577
00:41:21,040 --> 00:41:22,280
within ten days.

578
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,440
What is it, Hari?
Why are you giving him hope?

579
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:31,440
Fine..

580
00:41:32,040 --> 00:41:35,800
Forgive me if I was rude.

581
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:38,320
You did not mention your names.

582
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,280
My name is Harikrishnan.
- Okay.

583
00:41:40,760 --> 00:41:42,320
I am also Harikrishnan.

584
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:44,360
What is this?

585
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:45,480
This is nice.

586
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:48,480
You are both renowned advocates.

587
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:50,160
Is it the two of you?
- Yes..

588
00:41:50,240 --> 00:41:52,600
Why didn't you mention that?

589
00:41:53,720 --> 00:41:54,720
This is Ramappan.

590
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:57,240
He is a distant relative
from my mother's side.

591
00:41:57,320 --> 00:42:00,000
He has two children in Chennai.
One among them is a doctor.

592
00:42:00,080 --> 00:42:02,360
They are here on learning
of Guptan's demise.

593
00:42:02,440 --> 00:42:04,560
All of them grew up together.

594
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:06,200
As Guptan was crazy
about travelling

595
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:08,640
Ramappan and his kids
gave me company.

596
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:11,440
What do you want to know?
Ask me.

597
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:15,320
We wanted to be familiar
with Guptan's life.

598
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:17,960
We also wanted to know what
you had to say about him.

599
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:20,600
We got a few hints on our way here.

600
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:22,600
We came to know that
he was an introvert

601
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:24,760
and a very talented person.

602
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:26,520
We came to know that he sang well.

603
00:42:27,120 --> 00:42:28,880
What are you saying?

604
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:31,800
He just had to touch the Veena.

605
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:33,560
He would create divine music.

606
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,400
He was a poet, a singer

607
00:42:35,480 --> 00:42:38,320
a scholar and much more.

608
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,960
Didn't you notice
the decorations outside?

609
00:42:41,040 --> 00:42:42,400
Today is the festival of lights.

610
00:42:42,480 --> 00:42:44,760
The festival at the temple
also starts today.

611
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:49,680
This will be a festival
without my son for the first time.

612
00:42:51,960 --> 00:42:54,560
After the lamps are lit,
and the festival is started

613
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:57,880
venerations for the Goddess
will be performed for nine days.

614
00:42:58,200 --> 00:43:00,920
The Goddess will be pleased by
singing songs on the tenth day

615
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:04,000
and will be welcomed to our
home from the temple.

616
00:43:04,720 --> 00:43:06,200
My Guptan did that.

617
00:43:07,320 --> 00:43:09,040
My son would stand in front

618
00:43:09,120 --> 00:43:10,320
of the Goddess.

619
00:43:10,400 --> 00:43:12,840
I would bathe

620
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:15,400
and bless him wholeheartedly.

621
00:43:15,560 --> 00:43:18,360
As the rightful heir of the house

622
00:43:18,440 --> 00:43:19,720
he will let go of everything

623
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:23,240
including wealth
and power and become pure.

624
00:43:23,360 --> 00:43:24,600
He will become a nomad.

625
00:43:25,360 --> 00:43:28,680
The Goddess, pleased
by music and lights

626
00:43:28,760 --> 00:43:31,360
would permit us
to live for a year

627
00:43:31,440 --> 00:43:33,240
and return after
giving back the wealth.

628
00:43:33,320 --> 00:43:34,640
That is the custom here.

629
00:43:35,040 --> 00:43:36,760
Guptan had accepted the wealth

630
00:43:37,040 --> 00:43:39,480
and sang songs for the Goddess

631
00:43:39,920 --> 00:43:43,640
for the past 20 years.

632
00:43:46,600 --> 00:43:48,520
On the night of the tenth day
this year

633
00:43:48,600 --> 00:43:51,280
who is there to please
the Goddess with music?

634
00:43:54,280 --> 00:43:59,000
Whom shall I bless
as per tradition?

635
00:44:01,600 --> 00:44:03,760
Who will accept the wealth
from the Goddess?

636
00:44:05,880 --> 00:44:07,520
Please don't worry, your Majesty.

637
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:09,760
Guptan will come back.

638
00:44:11,520 --> 00:44:12,800
What are you saying?

639
00:44:13,600 --> 00:44:17,120
He said that he would bring
the one who murdered Guptan.

640
00:44:17,480 --> 00:44:19,840
Now you say that Guptan
will come back.

641
00:44:22,040 --> 00:44:23,000
Let him come.

642
00:44:24,120 --> 00:44:25,480
Even I want the same

643
00:44:25,520 --> 00:44:26,360
in my heart.

644
00:44:27,280 --> 00:44:30,200
I can't accept the fact
that he won't return.

645
00:44:30,320 --> 00:44:31,840
He will come, sir.
He will come.

646
00:44:33,160 --> 00:44:35,880
Hari wants to ask you
some questions.

647
00:44:36,200 --> 00:44:39,240
Yes. What do you
want to know? Ask me.

648
00:44:39,960 --> 00:44:42,280
Did Guptan have any close friends?

649
00:44:42,920 --> 00:44:45,160
He was a loner.

650
00:44:45,520 --> 00:44:48,960
He came with a few
college students recently

651
00:44:49,080 --> 00:44:50,400
and stayed for two days.

652
00:44:50,760 --> 00:44:53,760
The house was filled with music
and poetry. They had a good time.

653
00:44:54,280 --> 00:44:55,800
That's when I came to know

654
00:44:55,880 --> 00:44:58,680
that Guptan was a visiting
professor in some college.

655
00:44:58,760 --> 00:45:00,040
Which was the college?

656
00:45:02,040 --> 00:45:03,480
He mentioned some name.

657
00:45:03,720 --> 00:45:04,880
I forgot it.

658
00:45:05,400 --> 00:45:06,640
Can you try to remember it?

659
00:45:07,600 --> 00:45:10,200
No. I did not take it seriously.

660
00:45:10,480 --> 00:45:13,640
Was anyone else close to Guptan?

661
00:45:14,800 --> 00:45:15,640
Yes.

662
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:18,160
If Guptan was alive

663
00:45:18,400 --> 00:45:22,320
he would have been
married by this time.

664
00:45:22,720 --> 00:45:24,720
He never wanted to get married

665
00:45:24,800 --> 00:45:26,360
but he told me recently

666
00:45:26,440 --> 00:45:28,480
that a girl, who I might like

667
00:45:28,560 --> 00:45:31,960
would be with him
to celebrate this festival.

668
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:35,960
What did he say
about that girl?

669
00:45:36,360 --> 00:45:39,880
He just mentioned the name Mohini.

670
00:45:41,920 --> 00:45:44,280
Was it Mohini or Mira?

671
00:45:44,440 --> 00:45:47,920
No. It was Mohini.
Mohini Varma.

672
00:45:51,640 --> 00:45:53,880
What is it?
Why are you shocked? - No.

673
00:45:53,960 --> 00:45:55,120
It's nothing, sir.
- Okay.

674
00:45:55,200 --> 00:45:57,680
We want to visit
Guptan's bedroom and study room.

675
00:45:58,320 --> 00:46:01,000
Of course. The room is upstairs
on the east facing end.

676
00:46:01,080 --> 00:46:03,600
Nothing has been changed.
Everything is intact.

677
00:46:03,680 --> 00:46:05,280
Please proceed.
- Okay. - Yes.

678
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:17,320
His dad did not make a mistake.

679
00:46:17,440 --> 00:46:19,040
It was not Mira either.

680
00:46:19,120 --> 00:46:21,120
We were the ones who
made a mistake.

681
00:46:21,720 --> 00:46:23,960
Mohini Varma is not fictitious.

682
00:46:24,520 --> 00:46:27,840
I have found the letters
she wrote to Guptan.

683
00:46:28,400 --> 00:46:29,280
So have I.

684
00:46:39,120 --> 00:46:41,760
Mohini Varma is
part of a riddle.

685
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:45,000
She truly loved and admired Guptan.

686
00:46:45,320 --> 00:46:48,400
She is either equally talented
or may be better than Guptan.

687
00:46:49,040 --> 00:46:50,840
You may take these
and keep it there.

688
00:46:51,000 --> 00:46:52,000
Move it.

689
00:46:55,400 --> 00:46:56,600
What?
Did you see everything?

690
00:46:56,680 --> 00:46:58,440
Yes. We are leaving, sir.

691
00:46:58,560 --> 00:46:59,520
What is this?

692
00:46:59,600 --> 00:47:01,400
You came to my house
and are leaving

693
00:47:01,480 --> 00:47:04,560
without staying or having a meal..
- We have lots of work, sir.

694
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:09,160
We are taking the letters and
poems written by Mohini to Guptan.

695
00:47:09,240 --> 00:47:11,520
We will return it.
Do you mind? - No problem.

696
00:47:11,640 --> 00:47:15,040
But when you leave so soon..
- We will be back soon.

697
00:47:16,120 --> 00:47:18,520
Didn't I tell you?
This is Ramappan's son.

698
00:47:18,600 --> 00:47:19,760
Dr. Jaikumar.

699
00:47:29,480 --> 00:47:30,320
I am Hari.

700
00:47:32,760 --> 00:47:33,720
I am Krishnan.

701
00:47:35,600 --> 00:47:37,080
This is my brother, Premkumar.

702
00:47:38,080 --> 00:47:39,200
Hello.
- I'm Hari.

703
00:47:41,480 --> 00:47:42,280
I'm Krishnan.

704
00:47:44,200 --> 00:47:45,080
We shall leave.

705
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:13,520
What is it?
Are you here to question me?

706
00:48:13,640 --> 00:48:15,720
No. But we have to.

707
00:48:17,440 --> 00:48:20,520
Nice. This is the apt place
to dispel guilt.

708
00:48:22,200 --> 00:48:24,200
I'm asking you something
out of the blue.

709
00:48:25,240 --> 00:48:27,760
Did Guptan have another lover?

710
00:48:32,040 --> 00:48:33,280
Not another lover.

711
00:48:33,400 --> 00:48:35,080
He had only one lover.

712
00:48:36,080 --> 00:48:37,160
Mohini Varma.

713
00:48:40,240 --> 00:48:44,720
So you knew about Guptan
and Mohini Varma

714
00:48:45,080 --> 00:48:46,080
but you hid it.

715
00:48:46,960 --> 00:48:47,800
Why?

716
00:48:50,600 --> 00:48:51,840
What is this, Hari?

717
00:48:51,920 --> 00:48:54,440
Mira will have her own reasons.

718
00:48:54,880 --> 00:48:56,360
Mira loved Guptan.

719
00:48:56,480 --> 00:48:58,360
But Guptan loved Mohini.

720
00:48:58,560 --> 00:49:02,720
Any woman would lose her mind
when she knows that the guy

721
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:05,400
she loves is in love
with another woman.

722
00:49:05,520 --> 00:49:07,280
Yes.
- If you can't convince your lover

723
00:49:07,360 --> 00:49:09,320
you may even harm him.

724
00:49:09,440 --> 00:49:10,880
If you have a wealthy dad

725
00:49:10,960 --> 00:49:12,800
you may blame someone and escape.

726
00:49:12,880 --> 00:49:16,120
You may build and live in a
pretty cabin to dispel your guilt.

727
00:49:16,600 --> 00:49:18,960
When smart advocates
argue using these points

728
00:49:19,120 --> 00:49:20,160
you will be trapped.

729
00:49:21,960 --> 00:49:23,800
How were you related to Guptan

730
00:49:23,880 --> 00:49:26,760
who came to Poonoor after
accepting Mohini's invitation?

731
00:49:28,160 --> 00:49:30,280
I was only a friend

732
00:49:30,360 --> 00:49:32,200
who helped Guptan

733
00:49:32,760 --> 00:49:35,280
in finding Mohini,
whom he never met.

734
00:49:37,320 --> 00:49:38,920
Do you hear her, Hari?

735
00:49:39,160 --> 00:49:41,480
Mira and Guptan were just friends.

736
00:49:41,560 --> 00:49:42,600
Do you get it?

737
00:49:43,120 --> 00:49:46,960
Why did you spend a night
with him in a hotel?

738
00:49:48,680 --> 00:49:49,600
Shame on you!

739
00:49:51,280 --> 00:49:53,520
Two advocates who are
famous all over the nation.

740
00:49:53,800 --> 00:49:55,880
Now I know how narrow
your minds are.

741
00:49:56,600 --> 00:49:58,680
If Hari and Krishnan
share the same room

742
00:49:58,920 --> 00:50:00,400
is there anything immoral in it?

743
00:50:03,160 --> 00:50:06,680
You cannot believe
that a guy and a girl

744
00:50:07,160 --> 00:50:08,360
can spend time together morally.

745
00:50:08,480 --> 00:50:09,680
It's because you cannot
be like that.

746
00:50:11,800 --> 00:50:15,480
But Guptan could do that.
So could I.

747
00:50:19,000 --> 00:50:21,840
We discussed
Mohini's letters and poems.

748
00:50:22,560 --> 00:50:25,360
We spent a whole night
in the hotel room.

749
00:50:25,800 --> 00:50:26,600
It's true.

750
00:50:27,360 --> 00:50:31,960
But we shared his dreams
about Mohini.

751
00:50:33,240 --> 00:50:34,120
Not the bed.

752
00:50:36,960 --> 00:50:39,560
I've known Guptan
for just a few days.

753
00:50:40,320 --> 00:50:41,720
We became close
on our first meeting itself.

754
00:50:42,720 --> 00:50:44,120
The books we read were similar.

755
00:50:44,600 --> 00:50:45,480
We had like thoughts.

756
00:50:46,240 --> 00:50:48,960
Even the topics for our research
were the same.

757
00:50:49,760 --> 00:50:52,240
I wanted him to be my mentor.

758
00:50:53,040 --> 00:50:55,720
But he wanted us to be friends.

759
00:50:56,920 --> 00:50:57,920
You guys don't know

760
00:50:58,160 --> 00:51:00,440
who and what he was.

761
00:51:01,120 --> 00:51:01,920
We know some of it.

762
00:51:03,000 --> 00:51:07,240
Guptan was an eccentric who knew
the highs and lows of life.

763
00:51:09,120 --> 00:51:12,640
At the same time,
a great dreamer.

764
00:51:14,680 --> 00:51:16,440
While he was studying
for his MA in Indore

765
00:51:17,200 --> 00:51:19,560
Mohini was doing
her first year of her BA.

766
00:51:20,040 --> 00:51:23,360
She wrote many letters to Guptan
from Delhi.

767
00:51:23,960 --> 00:51:26,240
A poor girl who was trapped
by some people.

768
00:51:27,040 --> 00:51:28,080
It might be her husband

769
00:51:28,560 --> 00:51:29,760
or some gangsters.

770
00:51:30,040 --> 00:51:31,760
Anyway, she was held
in a gilded cage.

771
00:51:32,040 --> 00:51:33,680
She wrote many poems to escape
from the pain.

772
00:51:34,200 --> 00:51:35,320
She wanted a life with him.

773
00:51:35,760 --> 00:51:37,120
Guptan loved her poems.

774
00:51:37,480 --> 00:51:38,400
He loved her through them.

775
00:51:39,080 --> 00:51:42,200
He went to Poonoor
when she asked him to come.

776
00:51:43,360 --> 00:51:44,320
This is what we know.

777
00:51:45,480 --> 00:51:47,800
You know the rest.

778
00:51:49,160 --> 00:51:50,560
Even I know only this much.

779
00:51:51,360 --> 00:51:54,840
We went searching for her
in Poonoor.

780
00:51:56,040 --> 00:51:56,840
But we couldn't find her.

781
00:51:57,080 --> 00:51:58,760
She is hiding somewhere.

782
00:52:00,440 --> 00:52:01,680
I want to find her.

783
00:52:02,560 --> 00:52:04,880
I want to know why she invited him

784
00:52:05,720 --> 00:52:06,880
and made him fall in love.

785
00:52:07,840 --> 00:52:09,200
We should save her
if she is innocent.

786
00:52:09,760 --> 00:52:11,160
We should punish her
if she is found guilty.

787
00:52:11,920 --> 00:52:12,760
I am clear about one thing.

788
00:52:13,080 --> 00:52:15,680
If everyone comes to know that
the investigation is against her..

789
00:52:15,800 --> 00:52:20,600
She or the ones who are hiding
her might escape from here. - Yes.

790
00:52:21,680 --> 00:52:25,040
That is the reason
why you portrayed Gabriel

791
00:52:25,120 --> 00:52:28,120
as the culprit and hid everything,
isn't it? - Yes.

792
00:52:28,200 --> 00:52:30,560
You wish to keep her name

793
00:52:30,640 --> 00:52:33,840
out of this case.

794
00:52:34,600 --> 00:52:36,120
Yes.
- Okay.

795
00:52:36,920 --> 00:52:39,600
As we have started to understand
each other

796
00:52:40,160 --> 00:52:41,600
we would never stand against
your wishes.

797
00:52:42,280 --> 00:52:44,600
Apart from that

798
00:52:45,200 --> 00:52:48,120
we will find Mohini Varma for you
in nine days.

799
00:52:48,760 --> 00:52:50,240
Okay?
- Yes.

800
00:52:51,040 --> 00:52:53,560
But a lot of her letters
are missing.

801
00:52:53,800 --> 00:52:55,200
No. I have them.

802
00:52:55,320 --> 00:52:56,560
Can we see them?

803
00:52:56,960 --> 00:52:57,800
It's at home.

804
00:52:57,880 --> 00:52:58,840
Okay, then we will come
in the morning..

805
00:52:59,960 --> 00:53:01,280
Yes.. at 10 in the morning.

806
00:53:01,920 --> 00:53:02,800
Can we leave now?

807
00:53:04,200 --> 00:53:07,040
We know that some of our questions
may have bothered you.

808
00:53:07,320 --> 00:53:08,960
Which one?
The one about the bed?

809
00:53:09,800 --> 00:53:11,960
Well.. - Please forgive us, it's
the trait of being advocates.

810
00:53:12,120 --> 00:53:14,480
No hard feelings.
- Hey, never mind.

811
00:53:22,720 --> 00:53:27,640
So can we leave? - Okay, bye..
- See you.

812
00:53:31,680 --> 00:53:33,560
Why trouble that poor Gabriel..

813
00:53:34,320 --> 00:53:37,840
Can't you release him today itself?
- Sure..

814
00:54:08,000 --> 00:54:08,840
Why did you stop the car?

815
00:54:11,200 --> 00:54:14,000
You asked me to stop.
- Did I?

816
00:54:15,280 --> 00:54:16,720
You did, didn't you?
Why?

817
00:54:18,600 --> 00:54:19,920
I wanted to take a leak.

818
00:54:20,120 --> 00:54:21,240
Make it fast.
- Sure.

819
00:54:26,960 --> 00:54:30,160
Finally, I found out
that it was worth the long wait.

820
00:54:31,640 --> 00:54:35,000
Mira was born for me.

821
00:54:36,880 --> 00:54:40,080
I have to thank Ammalu
for everything.

822
00:54:40,640 --> 00:54:41,440
Her face..

823
00:54:43,360 --> 00:54:44,680
I felt that pinch of love

824
00:54:45,560 --> 00:54:47,720
at the very first sight.

825
00:54:48,240 --> 00:54:49,080
That closeness..

826
00:54:51,760 --> 00:54:56,360
Ammalu, thank you so much
for bringing Mira into my life.

827
00:54:56,960 --> 00:54:58,840
The tree which is shy to blossom.

828
00:55:00,800 --> 00:55:02,520
The day that forgot to end.

829
00:55:04,560 --> 00:55:07,600
It's like a new feeling found me.

830
00:55:09,400 --> 00:55:11,520
What's going on?
Are you flooding the place?

831
00:55:11,920 --> 00:55:13,040
It's been a while.
Aren't you done yet?

832
00:55:13,240 --> 00:55:14,440
I'm done..
I'm coming.

833
00:55:16,880 --> 00:55:20,120
I was thinking of getting
Gabriel out.

834
00:55:21,760 --> 00:55:22,640
Me too.

835
00:55:27,960 --> 00:55:29,440
Come..
- Come.

836
00:55:31,960 --> 00:55:33,280
A random college.

837
00:55:33,520 --> 00:55:34,600
A visiting professor
had taught there.

838
00:55:34,880 --> 00:55:38,200
He was a poet, vocalist,
philosopher and a gentleman.

839
00:55:39,120 --> 00:55:43,120
He was close with a six-member
gang of students.

840
00:55:44,240 --> 00:55:46,320
Which college was it?
Who was the professor?

841
00:55:46,960 --> 00:55:48,760
Who were the students?

842
00:55:49,280 --> 00:55:50,960
Find these out and report it
to Sundaran.

843
00:55:52,360 --> 00:55:56,640
All information from Chennai Agency
will be strictly confidential.

844
00:55:57,280 --> 00:56:00,400
It should only be handled by Hari,
Sundaran and me.

845
00:56:00,560 --> 00:56:01,520
Okay?
- Okay.

846
00:56:03,760 --> 00:56:04,560
Read this.

847
00:56:06,840 --> 00:56:08,680
Who monitors the data
from Chennai? - Stephen does.

848
00:56:09,680 --> 00:56:10,760
Should we ask anything of Mira?

849
00:56:11,240 --> 00:56:12,320
I think we don't have to.

850
00:56:12,640 --> 00:56:16,040
Yes. Her thoughts and decisions
are strange.

851
00:56:16,680 --> 00:56:18,600
Then again, it has helped us
to a certain extent.

852
00:56:18,640 --> 00:56:21,680
How? - Isn't it because of her
suing Gabriel

853
00:56:21,760 --> 00:56:22,800
that Ammalu summoned us?

854
00:56:22,880 --> 00:56:23,760
Didn't it pan out well?

855
00:56:24,120 --> 00:56:25,960
Yes.. I've promised
to meet with her tomorrow.

856
00:56:26,240 --> 00:56:28,080
Yes. We will meet her
tomorrow at 10 a.m.

857
00:56:28,160 --> 00:56:29,360
Yes. Maybe around 10:30 a.m.

858
00:56:39,880 --> 00:56:40,680
Drat!

859
00:56:49,800 --> 00:56:51,320
Krishnan!
- Yes?

860
00:57:07,920 --> 00:57:08,720
Mira is mine!
- Mira is mine!

861
00:57:13,880 --> 00:57:15,800
Fantastic! Great!

862
00:57:16,440 --> 00:57:18,200
Great, indeed!
- Isn't it?

863
00:57:18,280 --> 00:57:21,360
So Mira is mine!
- No. Mira is mine alone.

864
00:57:21,680 --> 00:57:22,600
Stop kidding.

865
00:57:22,880 --> 00:57:25,320
I decided
when I saw her up close.

866
00:57:25,440 --> 00:57:29,720
I made the decision when I
saw her from a distance.

867
00:57:30,920 --> 00:57:32,040
Stop joking, Krishnan.

868
00:57:32,560 --> 00:57:34,680
I'm serious.
- I'm even more serious.

869
00:57:35,120 --> 00:57:35,960
Quit it, will you?

870
00:57:36,440 --> 00:57:38,560
I know that you
are pulling my strings. - No.

871
00:57:39,000 --> 00:57:40,520
I'm saying this from
the bottom of my heart.

872
00:57:40,840 --> 00:57:41,880
Mira is mine!

873
00:57:41,960 --> 00:57:43,160
No! She is mine!

874
00:57:43,240 --> 00:57:44,760
Am I not older by a year or so?

875
00:57:44,800 --> 00:57:47,920
That is based on the records.
You are much older.. - Leave it..

876
00:57:48,000 --> 00:57:49,440
It has already been decided.
- Yes.

877
00:57:49,520 --> 00:57:50,800
It is!

878
00:57:50,880 --> 00:57:53,840
If Kallookkaran Vishwambharan
has a daughter named Mira

879
00:57:54,680 --> 00:57:57,760
she is mine! She's for advocate
Harikrishnan alias Krishnan!

880
00:57:58,040 --> 00:58:00,440
You can kiss your dreams goodbye.

881
00:58:00,720 --> 00:58:05,040
Krishnan, if I am Hari
of Harikrishnans Associates

882
00:58:05,360 --> 00:58:06,600
I won't kiss anything goodbye

883
00:58:06,920 --> 00:58:08,200
and no guy named Krishnan
is going to get

884
00:58:08,560 --> 00:58:10,640
Vishwambharan's daughter Mira.

885
00:58:13,640 --> 00:58:16,280
Key..
- Thank you..

886
00:58:17,240 --> 00:58:19,800
Okay.
So you love Mira.

887
00:58:20,120 --> 00:58:21,560
Yes.
- How much?

888
00:58:21,840 --> 00:58:24,360
A lot.
- Is it as vast as the sky?

889
00:58:25,840 --> 00:58:28,960
Yes. - So your love for her
is as vast as the sky.

890
00:58:29,120 --> 00:58:30,920
Now ask me how much I love her.

891
00:58:31,440 --> 00:58:33,280
Ask me.
- I'm not going to.

892
00:58:33,360 --> 00:58:34,960
Why?
- I prefer not to. - Hey!

893
00:58:35,040 --> 00:58:36,640
Why are you being a baby about it?

894
00:58:37,800 --> 00:58:39,640
Mira is the only girl
for me in this lifetime.

895
00:58:39,720 --> 00:58:40,520
Mine too.
- Okay.

896
00:58:48,720 --> 00:58:50,240
Krishnan, this is meant to be.

897
00:58:51,040 --> 00:58:54,320
Or else why didn't I even think
of even getting married?

898
00:58:54,680 --> 00:58:55,640
That's because you couldn't
find a girl!

899
00:58:56,040 --> 00:58:57,960
Me? Really?

900
00:58:59,760 --> 00:59:01,880
Who do you think you are?
Prince Charming?

901
00:59:02,680 --> 00:59:04,680
What girl in her right mind
will be attracted

902
00:59:04,760 --> 00:59:06,800
by your crooked teeth,
gummy smile

903
00:59:07,040 --> 00:59:09,600
those giant nasal openings
and your horsey gait?

904
00:59:15,520 --> 00:59:18,320
What?
- Girls will fly down from Egypt

905
00:59:18,360 --> 00:59:19,400
and line up for you on seeing

906
00:59:19,800 --> 00:59:21,960
your pumpkin-like cheeks,
squishy nose

907
00:59:22,000 --> 00:59:23,960
and your lopsided gait.

908
00:59:24,840 --> 00:59:26,840
Cover that nose, Krishnan.

909
00:59:27,000 --> 00:59:28,880
Let some girls look at your face.

910
00:59:29,200 --> 00:59:32,000
Enough..
Don't overdo it..

911
00:59:55,640 --> 00:59:56,800
Oh, sorry.

912
00:59:57,120 --> 00:59:58,240
What is this special ritual?

913
00:59:58,880 --> 01:00:00,600
This was taught to me
by my grandmother.

914
01:00:00,880 --> 01:00:03,400
To find answers to
unanswerable questions.

915
01:00:03,480 --> 01:00:04,400
How do you do it?

916
01:00:04,560 --> 01:00:09,440
If the leaf falls on 'Yes',
I'll meet Mohini Varma.

917
01:00:09,960 --> 01:00:11,200
But the leaf fell on 'No'.

918
01:00:11,520 --> 01:00:13,080
It means I am not going
to meet Mohini.

919
01:00:13,400 --> 01:00:14,440
It has never gone wrong.

920
01:00:15,000 --> 01:00:17,720
Harikrishnans cannot bring
Mohini Varma in front of me.

921
01:00:18,240 --> 01:00:19,120
Let's see.

922
01:00:19,200 --> 01:00:21,000
You can try.
But it is not going to happen.

923
01:00:21,560 --> 01:00:23,280
Let me clean it.
Nobody is supposed to see this.

924
01:00:24,400 --> 01:00:25,320
Take your seat.

925
01:00:25,760 --> 01:00:26,640
Let's have a cup of tea.

926
01:00:27,240 --> 01:00:28,640
You are well prepared, Mira.

927
01:00:29,480 --> 01:00:30,680
We are friends now.

928
01:00:31,200 --> 01:00:32,760
We are more than friends.
- Yes, even more than that.

929
01:00:35,960 --> 01:00:37,360
Can we see the letters and poems
written by Mohini?

930
01:00:38,360 --> 01:00:39,920
I will give it to you.
Please sit down.

931
01:00:41,080 --> 01:00:43,720
People need to have good taste
in literature to enjoy poetry.

932
01:00:43,920 --> 01:00:46,320
Yes.. I have good knowledge
of literature since childhood.

933
01:00:52,840 --> 01:00:53,680
I am sorry.

934
01:01:01,680 --> 01:01:02,880
No. I will clean it.

935
01:01:35,400 --> 01:01:36,400
Oh, no.

936
01:01:40,560 --> 01:01:41,400
I am sorry.

937
01:01:41,880 --> 01:01:44,960
You have spilt it, too.
You are similar to each other.

938
01:02:00,720 --> 01:02:01,760
Have your tea.

939
01:02:02,240 --> 01:02:03,880
It's really hot.
Let it cool down.

940
01:02:04,680 --> 01:02:07,320
I started to boil tea like this
after I met Guptan.

941
01:02:08,200 --> 01:02:11,320
He used to love having tea
when it was served hot.

942
01:02:13,200 --> 01:02:15,520
These are the letters and poems
written by Mohini.

943
01:02:36,520 --> 01:02:37,320
Have your tea.

944
01:02:55,200 --> 01:02:59,520
Guptan had set aside the most
beautiful 20 poems from Mohini.

945
01:03:00,440 --> 01:03:03,080
He wanted to publish them with her
permission after meeting her.

946
01:03:04,800 --> 01:03:09,160
We can't publish these poems
without her permission.

947
01:03:10,040 --> 01:03:14,600
It would be a great loss
to Malayalam literature

948
01:03:15,240 --> 01:03:17,960
if they don't get published.

949
01:03:19,360 --> 01:03:23,400
Your wish to adorn Malayalam
literature with these poems

950
01:03:23,560 --> 01:03:25,600
will be fulfilled at any cost.

951
01:03:25,840 --> 01:03:30,320
I will be the one to do..
- We will do it for you.

952
01:03:33,920 --> 01:03:38,080
I hope you can accomplish this
as soon as possible.

953
01:03:38,560 --> 01:03:40,920
We badly want to accomplish
that.

954
01:03:41,960 --> 01:03:42,960
Yes, we will do it.

955
01:03:43,800 --> 01:03:45,880
Mira, we are taking these poems
with us.

956
01:03:46,000 --> 01:03:47,360
Don't lose it somewhere.
- I won't.

957
01:03:48,320 --> 01:03:49,440
Mira.
- Yes.

958
01:03:50,280 --> 01:03:53,920
Which wood did you use
to make that bridge?

959
01:03:54,320 --> 01:03:55,240
Which bridge?

960
01:03:55,800 --> 01:03:56,960
That one.
Please come here.

961
01:03:58,160 --> 01:03:58,960
Mira, one minute.

962
01:03:59,400 --> 01:04:01,800
Did you make these house
based on ancient architecture

963
01:04:01,880 --> 01:04:04,240
or according to the techniques
used by the Japanese?

964
01:04:04,320 --> 01:04:07,120
It's an ordinary..
- Mira.

965
01:04:07,840 --> 01:04:11,520
Where did you get that
Mexican snow flower? Please come.

966
01:04:11,760 --> 01:04:15,240
Krishnan. We need to go.
We have work to do. Come on.

967
01:04:18,760 --> 01:04:20,480
Okay, bye.

968
01:04:22,960 --> 01:04:25,240
Even though we met
during a legal battle

969
01:04:25,960 --> 01:04:28,560
but we have a relationship..
- Hari, we should go.

970
01:04:28,600 --> 01:04:30,920
We have work to do.
- Yes. We need to go.

971
01:04:32,520 --> 01:04:36,680
You can expect any kind of help
from me.

972
01:04:36,920 --> 01:04:39,400
It can be anything.
- As a friend, he will help you.

973
01:04:39,480 --> 01:04:41,720
Yes. As a friend, I will help you.
- Yes, as a friend.

974
01:04:42,200 --> 01:04:43,640
As a friend.
- Yes, as a friend.

975
01:04:52,920 --> 01:04:56,960
When I offered to help Mira
whenever she needs me

976
01:04:57,200 --> 01:04:59,640
why was it necessary to bring
friendship in between that?

977
01:05:00,080 --> 01:05:00,880
Yes, it is necessary.

978
01:05:00,960 --> 01:05:05,360
It is not right to talk to a girl
like that.

979
01:05:05,480 --> 01:05:07,000
What is wrong?
- It is wrong.

980
01:05:07,640 --> 01:05:10,440
It is a vulgar statement.
- Let it be vulgar.

981
01:05:10,480 --> 01:05:12,240
I was talking to Mira,
not to your wife.

982
01:05:12,720 --> 01:05:14,160
What if I marry her in future?

983
01:05:14,240 --> 01:05:16,400
She will get married.
But she will be my wife.

984
01:05:16,760 --> 01:05:19,080
Don't talk nonsense.
- Who is talking nonsense now?

985
01:05:19,360 --> 01:05:23,280
You are the one who claimed a girl
as his wife without her consent.

986
01:05:23,480 --> 01:05:25,680
I said that. Don't talk to me
again, Krishnan.

987
01:05:25,880 --> 01:05:27,960
You can leave, Krishnan. I will
take care of this case. - No.

988
01:05:28,080 --> 01:05:29,720
You can leave. I will take care
of this alone.

989
01:05:29,800 --> 01:05:32,240
This case is related to my sister.
I will take care of it.

990
01:05:32,440 --> 01:05:33,840
I didn't transfer this case to you.

991
01:05:34,000 --> 01:05:36,360
Harikrishnan Associates
are not related to this case.

992
01:05:36,880 --> 01:05:40,480
It's true. Let's stop this company
forever from today.

993
01:05:40,640 --> 01:05:44,320
We are departing forever.
Harikrishnan Associates is closed.

994
01:05:44,360 --> 01:05:45,360
But I will take care of this case.

995
01:05:45,680 --> 01:05:47,880
Let's see
who will plead this case.

996
01:05:48,120 --> 01:05:48,960
Let's see.

997
01:05:49,440 --> 01:05:50,240
Yes. Let's see.

998
01:06:08,360 --> 01:06:10,400
Will you take photographs
of people travelling in cars?

999
01:06:10,880 --> 01:06:12,280
I will.
Hari!

