- Come on. Go to your seats.

1347
01:32:08,880 --> 01:32:10,080
Look here, everyone.

1348
01:32:10,280 --> 01:32:11,640
I am going to say everything.

1349
01:32:12,040 --> 01:32:13,320
All of you go to your seats.

1350
