- Okay.

1367
01:33:01,840 --> 01:33:03,920
Okay.
Was that a joke?

1368
01:33:04,040 --> 01:33:05,000
Laugh, everyone.

1369
01:33:05,080 --> 01:33:06,240
Or I will laugh myself.

1370
01:33:07,760 --> 01:33:10,800
Even if my daughter
gives birth 16 times

1371
01:33:10,960 --> 01:33:13,360
