1413
01:35:32,880 --> 01:35:36,080
That's why I am sending them
to Athipuzha tomorrow.

1414
01:35:36,440 --> 01:35:37,680
They won't come back.

1415
01:35:37,960 --> 01:35:40,000
I am here to apologise
for their actions

1416
01:35:40,080 --> 01:35:40,920
