01:36:27,280 --> 01:36:29,040
What?
- No.

1431
01:36:29,360 --> 01:36:31,360
Yes.
- What? - No.

1432
01:36:31,920 --> 01:36:34,520
What?
- Yes. - No.

1433
01:36:34,680 --> 01:36:35,640
Okay.

1434
01:36:43,160 --> 01:36:44,680
This office needs
only two people now.

1435
01:36:44,800 --> 01:36:46,360
The rest can go to the head office.

1436
01:36:46,720 --> 01:36:48,320
You should take care of everything
and come there.

1437
01:36:48,600 --> 01:36:50,200
My daughter and her husband
are coming from Singapore.

1438
01:36:50,520 --> 01:36:52,480
Let them come.

1439
01:37:06,640 --> 01:37:09,080
I haven't leaked anything
about your journey.

1440
01:37:09,880 --> 01:37:11,480
In this journey to find
Mohini Varma

1441
01:37:11,840 --> 01:37:13,600
I want to come with you.

1442
01:37:14,480 --> 01:37:16,920
We can't be sure about the leak.

1443
01:37:17,440 --> 01:37:18,960
Since you came here prepared

1444
01:37:19,320 --> 01:37:21,040
we can't stop you.

1445
01:37:21,160 --> 01:37:23,200
We don't know how long or where

1446
01:37:23,600 --> 01:37:25,320
we are going to stay.

1447
01:37:25,680 --> 01:37:26,520
That's all right.

1448
01:37:26,840 --> 01:37:28,840
Get in.

1449
01:37:45,480 --> 01:37:49,600
Okay. At this rate,
we can decide soon enough.

1450
01:37:54,440 --> 01:37:57,840
Thomas Mathew, Stephen,
Radhakrishnan

1451
01:37:58,040 --> 01:38:00,640
Sudarsanan, Cletus, Basheer.

1452
01:38:00,760 --> 01:38:02,480
These are the six people.

1453
01:38:03,320 --> 01:38:06,840
But the connection of them
to a Mohini Varma

1454
01:38:07,320 --> 01:38:08,320
is not something we know.

1455
01:38:09,040 --> 01:38:10,480
After the murder of Mr. Guptan

1456
01:38:10,840 --> 01:38:13,240
none of this six people
has come back to the hostel.

1457
01:38:14,000 --> 01:38:15,960
As their warden,
what do you say, sir?

1458
01:38:16,400 --> 01:38:17,800
I asked their families.

1459
01:38:18,320 --> 01:38:20,960
