1463
01:38:27,320 --> 01:38:28,760
We don't know that.

1464
01:38:29,840 --> 01:38:30,920
Okay.

1465
01:38:31,400 --> 01:38:33,160
Thank you, sir.
- Welcome. - Thank you very much.

1466
01:38:36,080 --> 01:38:37,360
Okay.
Thank you very much.

1467
