and inform us.

1471
01:38:53,640 --> 01:38:55,200
Only then can we go forward.

1472
01:38:56,280 --> 01:38:57,560
We are staying
at the guest house here.

1473
01:38:57,880 --> 01:38:58,920
We will eat from the hotel.

1474
01:39:03,480 --> 01:39:04,960
You had promised
that you would bring

1475
01:39:05,320 --> 01:39:07,560
