1476
01:39:10,040 --> 01:39:11,960
There are only three days left now.

1477
01:39:12,440 --> 01:39:15,720
Yes. The festival in Killikal
temple is only three days away.

1478
01:39:16,520 --> 01:39:18,040
I have a lot promises to fulfil
on that day.

1479
01:39:18,920 --> 01:39:20,920
But we need these six people
who are the last clue.

1480
01:39:21,120 --> 01:39:23,160
They reached Poonoor the day before

1481
01:39:23,840 --> 01:39:24,960
Guptan arrived.

1482
01:39:27,920 --> 01:39:29,200
In Hotel Vrindavan

1483
01:39:29,360 --> 01:39:31,760
